21 October 2014Deputy Minister of Communications Stella Ndabeni-Abrahams will on Thursday 23 October 2014 host stakeholder engagement in Kimberly, Northern Cape. This visit which will encompass sessions with government communicators and the media is a continuation of the Deputy Minister s efforts to engage with sector stakeholders in various provinces. To date the Deputy Minister has held engagements in six provinces.Members of the Media are invited as follows:Media Programme09h00 Arrival and Registration11h00 - Engagement with MediaVenue - Protea Hotel, Kimberley Big Hole, West Circular RoadMedia enquiries and RSVPs Nthabeleng Mokitimi E-mail: nthabeleng@gcis.gov.za Cell: 081 308 0193Issued by Department of Communications